###############################################################################
# Perception Valuation
###############################################################################

This file introduces the abstract notion of a derived valuation
specific to perceptual alignment.

Perception valuation evaluates the stability and coherence
of perceptual agreement, not the correctness of perception.

It does NOT:
• judge truth or falsity
• invalidate personal experience
• imply authority or intervention
###############################################################################
-/

namespace SigmaR

/--
An abstract derived valuation associated with perceptual
agreement and alignment.
-/
constant PerceptionValuation : Type

end SigmaR
